comment: Lopez (CHI) is in the paint without actively guarding an opponent for longer than three seconds.
Grant (CHI) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Payton (ORL) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Grant (CHI) gets his hand on the ball and any contact with Fournier (ORL) is incidental.
Biyombo (ORL) makes incidental contact with Lauvergne (CHI) during rebounding.
Lauvergne (CHI) jumps vertically contesting Ross' (ORL) driving shot attempt.
Payton (ORL) makes incidental contact with Rondo (CHI) that does not affect his FOM off ball.
Payton (ORL) allows Butler (CHI) to land following the jump shot attempt.
[Observable in enhanced video] Ross (ORL) moves his pivot foot.
Payton (ORL) maintains legal guarding position on the drive to the basket by Grant (CHI) and cleanly strips the ball.
Rondo (CHI) inbounds the ball within 5 seconds.
Ross (ORL) legally contests Grant's (CHI) jump shot attempt.
Grant (CHI) commits a take foul on Gordon (ORL).
Rondo (CHI) commits a take foul on Fournier (ORL).
Fournier (ORL) briefly clamps Lopez' (CHI) arm but does not affect his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Grant (CHI) commits a take foul on Fournier (ORL).
